tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE car_models (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer_id INT,
    maintenance_schedule TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE CarModels (model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,model_name VARCHAR(255),manufacturer_id INT,maintenance_schedule_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE Manufacturers (manufacturer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,manufacturer_name VARCHAR(255),year_founded INT) 

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceSchedules (maintenance_schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,maintenance_type VARCHAR(255),description TEXT) 

CREATE TABLE Cars (car_id INT PRIMARY KEY,model_id INT,manufacturer_id INT,year_made INT,license_plate VARCHAR(20)) 

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceLogs (log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,car_id INT,maintenance_schedule_id INT,date_performed DATE)
